        <textarea id="textInput" rows="4" placeholder="Example: A futuristic city at sunset with neon lights, flying cars, and a sense of innovation. Create a motivational tech video.">A breathtaking sunset over a serene lake with mountains in the background, birds flying across golden clouds. Calm, inspiring, and high quality.</textarea>

        <div class="flex-group">
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>🎨 Video Style</label>
