            <p style="color:#334155;">Our Text-to-Video tool uses generative effects to produce high-quality video in real-time. Choose from five distinct visual styles with text overlays, dynamic gradient backgrounds, and motion elements. Customize duration & mood.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#fff; border-radius: 24px; padding: 20px; flex:1;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 8px;">💰 Monetization Ready</h3>
