    <footer>
        <p>© 2025 AI VideoGen — Transform text into video stories. For professional use, high quality output simulation. SEO optimized meta tags, fast loading, and accessible.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 10px;">⭐ Generate unlimited previews | Supports modern browsers | Fully responsive design</p>
